    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331150/extras/5b960df03bc14db80fb3de90583d04e9.poster.avif?t=1751879089\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331150/extras/5b960df03bc14db80fb3de90583d04e9.webm?t=1751879089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331150/extras/5b960df03bc14db80fb3de90583d04e9.mp4?t=1751879089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mystery and Intrigue</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A town is being bled dry by a hidden cult, and every drop of blood fuels their dark magic. Tear through their ranks before they amass enough blood to usher in a new world order.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kill Them All</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Dominic, a man with the unique ability to eject blades from his wrists, and Darius, a mage that picks up the blood of fallen foes and uses it to cast devastating magic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use each character's unique skill set to slash, stab, punch, and beam your way through the cult's compounds. Use stealth tactics to get the jump on your enemies, or confront them head on, odds be damned. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331150/extras/fec5e322cf0a7b4e8118cf2b55515e05.poster.avif?t=1751879089\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331150/extras/fec5e322cf0a7b4e8118cf2b55515e05.webm?t=1751879089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331150/extras/fec5e322cf0a7b4e8118cf2b55515e05.mp4?t=1751879089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the beginning of Dominic's story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play 9 of the game's 57 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as 2 of the game's 7 characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the game's first 3 bosses</p></li></ul>",
